snippet.title: Little Kitty, Big City - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Little Kitty, Big City is coming to Nintendo Switch next year! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/little-kitty-big-city-switch/

Will you make your way home or will you explore what the big city has to offer first? I mean, getting home is obviously your main priority. Obviously. Well, it's one of your priorities. Maybe more of a guideline... It's definitely on your To-Do list somewhere! But first? Exploration!

#LittleKittyBigCity #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch
